Remember to log out before accessing remotely to the Raspberry. (or it will work wierdly)
Wi-Fi coverage should also be the best possible as it will not work properly if Wi-Fi coverage is bad.


When you finish using it remember also to logout.
-----
install

sudo apt update
sudo apt-get install raspberrypi-ui-mods xinit xserver-xorg

sudo reboot

sudo apt install xrdp 

systemctl show -p SubState --value xrdp
sudo adduser xrdp ssl-cert  
